descriptionText: Dan Wahlin runs through the type of things attendees can expect to see and learn at Angular U in June 2015
title: Dan Wahlin Giving Us an Idea of What to Expect at Angular U

title: Travis  Tidwell Talking About MEAN and IOT

title: Brad Green Talks About Angular U

title: Ward Bell Talking MEAN session preview

descriptionText: ECMAScript6 is what Angular 2 is built on.  Scott Moss is doing a full workshop on EcmaScript both Wendesday and Thursday of Angular U.
title: Scott Moss Talks About His ECMAScript6 Workshops

descriptionText: Databinding is a significant improvement in Angular 2 over what is in Angular 1.x.  Learn from Misko, the father of Angular what the changes are and why they are so important.
title: Misko Hevery Talks About Databinding in Angular 2

descriptionText: Brad Green, who runs the Google Angular team talks about (among other things) how Angular 2 improves on directives and controllers with components.
title: Brad Green Talks Directives, Controllers become Components in Angular 2
